  "title": "Junior/Senior Cloud Operations Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Implement, maintain, and administer IT infrastructure including networks, operating systems, storage, and backup systems</li><li>Collaborate with system development teams on system design, implementation, integration, and testing</li><li>Provide 24x7 on-call support on a rotational basis, including executing corrective actions to resolve production issues and minimize system downtime</li><li>Develop and maintain technical and program documentation to support effective planning and execution</li><li>Liaise with customers and external vendors to troubleshoot and resolve technical issues</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum of 3–5 years of relevant working experience</li><li>Solid understanding of IT infrastructure, including operating systems and networking</li><li>Strong interest in emerging technologies and a willingness to continuously upgrade skillsets<br /></li></ul><p><p><strong>Work Location: </strong>Tampines</p><p>(EA Reg No: 20C0312)</p><p>Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>qianyu@talentsis.com.sg </strong>for immediate processing.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p></p>",
